com.cloudera.cdk.data.hbase.manager
Class DefaultSchemaManager

java.lang.Object
  com.cloudera.cdk.data.hbase.manager.DefaultSchemaManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
SchemaManager
public class DefaultSchemaManager
extends Object
implements SchemaManager

The Default SchemaManager implementation. It uses a ManagedSchemaDao implementation, passed in the constructor, to read schema metadata, and persist schema metadata for schema creations and migrations.
